{"title":"相片","authors":["星火"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"相片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘屋里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上挂满相片："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的挎着冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺立在海防前线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的两鬓染上银霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩膀上有着少将军衔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在炼钢炉前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧握着长长的钢钎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的坐在拖拉机上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手转动着方向盘……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少张呵多少张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令人眼花缭乱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有些莫名其妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙去追问根源："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您有多少亲友？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您有多少儿男？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘只是微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迟迟地不肯答言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪明的小孙女儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手指着锦旗一面——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，我忽然觉得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房间里红光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“子弟兵的妈妈”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六个大字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像红霞飞起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌灿烂！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}